{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/fe/2020/05/07/从RN到Flutter-状态管理.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"9c756984-ff2e-5b3e-9e38-35c11c58ea0e","excerpt":"从 RN 到 Flutter-状态管理 状态机是部件在生命期同步访问的信息。Flutter 使用实现状态管理。 StatelessWidget Flutter…","html":"<h1>从 RN 到 Flutter-状态管理</h1>\n<p>状态机是部件在生命期同步访问的信息。Flutter 使用<code class=\"language-text\">StatefulWidget</code>实现状态管理。</p>\n<h2>StatelessWidget</h2>\n<p>Flutter 中，一个<code class=\"language-text\">StatelessWidget</code>不需要管理内部状态。</p>\n<p>一个无状态部件对于不依赖于非默认设置和通过<code class=\"language-text\">BuildContext</code>传入的情况下的用户界面非常有用。</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">AboutDialog</code>、<code class=\"language-text\">CircleAvater</code>和<code class=\"language-text\">Text</code>都是<code class=\"language-text\">StatelessWidget</code>的子类。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"dart\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-dart line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-dart\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"package:flutter/material.dart\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token function\">runApp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">MyWidget</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Stateless Example\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">MyWidget</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">StatelessWidget</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">final</span> String text<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">MyWidget</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Key key<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token metadata symbol\">@required</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>text <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">super</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>key<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> key<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    Widget <span class=\"token function\">build</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>BuildContext context<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">Center</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n            child<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">Text</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n                text<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                textDirection<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> TextDirection<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ltr<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>上面的例子传入<code class=\"language-text\">text</code>到<code class=\"language-text\">MyWidget</code>类的构造器，并以<code class=\"language-text\">final</code>标注。这个类基于<code class=\"language-text\">StatelessWidget</code>——它包含不变数据。</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">build</code>方法会在以下三种情况下执行：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>当部件加入到一个树中</li>\n<li>当部件的父部件变化</li>\n<li>当它继承的部件变化</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>StatefulWidget</h2>","frontmatter":{"category":"fe"},"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2020/05/07/从RN到Flutter-状态管理.html","date":"May 07, 2020","title":"从RN到Flutter-状态管理"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/fe/2020/05/07/从RN到Flutter-状态管理.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2020/05/06/spacedesk让任意一台设备成为扩展屏幕.html","title":"spacedesk让任意一台设备成为扩展屏幕"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tech"}},"next":null}}}